snippet.title: Memories of Mars - Dev Diary 01 - The Cloning Facility
snippet.description:
Welcome to Mars! Take a look inside the cloning facility and get to know a bit more about Memories of Mars.

Be sure to sign up at http://www.memoriesofmars.com to get an exclusive camo pattern and a blueprint of a rifle. Offer expires at launch.

Subscribe and stay tuned for future videos about Memories of Mars at www.memoriesofmars.com

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MemoriesOfMars
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MemoriesOfMars

Our Steam discussion page is found here: http://steamcommunity.com/app/644290/discussions/
